# No ForgeMap (for now)

ForgeMap and the in-app mapper experiment are **cancelled**. Do not restore Lua/Java mapper code, MAP buttons, or forgemap plugins unless the user explicitly starts a new mapper project.

- Old profiles may still mention `forgemap` — `PluginParser` skips that plugin; optionally run `scripts/strip_forgemap_from_profile.py`.
- Keep **btTest** and **production** feature-parity for core client work (no mapper-only features in test).
